Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,an island with two parts, one burning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After learning about the ruler of the island -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar clown, aka the Master's motive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and all while trying to escape Land of the Dead, the weapon of mass destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,along with their pirate ally -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the Warlord - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they are on the move to kidnap Caesar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,save the children, and escape from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What tremendous hidden strength he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But falling through here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,will land him in the slide to the garbage dump deep underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll never be able to come back up unless he can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect him to sabotage himself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was pretty sure that I could take my heart back from Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't expect you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Vergo-san to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have to be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:59.99,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Fists Collide! A Battle of the Two Vice Admirals!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:11.96,"Sign",,0,0,0,,B BUILDING 3RD FLOOR - BISCUITS ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha, those sweet candies are for everybody, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Share and eat them together as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't eat them anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a difficult girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we don't have any time for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about you people so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The infamous Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Monet, a Snow-Snow Fruit eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to restrain the children here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, go find some Sea Prism Stone handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Prism Stone handcuffs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy asked me to find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me to find things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to find Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:50.96,"Sign",,0,0,0,,D BUILDING - THE "SAD" MANUFACTURING ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This room's really disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you looking away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just shut up and grovel on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Vergo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the soldiers to know the truth about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They admire you like a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a serious breach of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you're Joker's dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw them a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're heating up, Smoker-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you're worrying about those Navy misfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a base commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do whatever I want to my good-for-nothing subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, you're gonna have to die anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,since you know who I really am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you've known them for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and even if you're a base commander
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which I don't acknowledge now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,once we're out of the base,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,an unit commander is responsible for the troops' life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lay a hand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,on my men!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:38.83,"Sign",,0,0,0,,B BUILDING - THE G-5 AND SANJI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no place to step!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry the injured and let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta protect Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so friendly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how people would define our relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But pirates are free!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When you gave the Vergo impostor a blow, brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you looked so cool - even I could fall in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you looked so hot, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I don't need support from guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling a pirate "brother"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The tank exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It caught fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a crack on the outer wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Another explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The gas is flowing in from the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadly gas from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Run if you don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This B Building is very big
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but it'll be filled up with the gas in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tashigi-chan, you have to lead them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose your way, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna die if you're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:35.88,"Sign",,0,0,0,,R BUILDING 2ND FLOOR - THE SECRET ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They let Land of the Dead in themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...letting them die there won't help
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,bring my experiment show to completion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, close the gates to Building C and D!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. What about the one to R?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that one open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to lure them into the first floor of R Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to get to R Building - gate 66 anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want them to take an unnecessary side trip
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's just guide them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.59,"Sign",,0,0,0,,C BUILDING - A GARBAGE DUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So is this a garbage dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I fell all the way down to the deep underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I had been running for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, you insolent fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't like this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The "secret room" on the second floor of R Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't wanna come to this shitty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't let the Straw Hats do whatever they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They pushed it a little too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got Joker on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they come this far, I'll kill them all perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been ready to fight since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did you summon us here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to the former office of that despicable Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk is also an enemy to us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,since he caused the accident four years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we fight them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You people are the best soldiers I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to shed your blood for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let me explain about the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When we close the gates to C and D as I said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the only open paths left
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,are the ones connected
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to the first floor of R Building which is below this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats, the G-5, or the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter if they're our enemies or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the only place those survivors can get to is going to be the room below.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some air vents on the first floor of R Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can let the air from outside - that is to say, Land of the Dead - flow in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there is no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can survive that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When we close all the gates,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it will become a big gas chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna broadcast what's going on in that room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the underground brokers in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So they will see what I'm capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pardon me for asking this, Master Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you create that deadly poison gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Vegapunk's poison gas
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that spread all over the island after the accident four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it freaks us out, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...an avenging battle of science!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...the mad scientist -
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"No! If such a weapon explodes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what's gonna happen to the people on the island?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop it, Vegapunk!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But the accident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he still lords over us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as the head of the science department of the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's considered the world's greatest scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tolerate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the cruel man who hurt you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's right that people still call him the No.1 scientist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to prove them wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to make a weapon of mass destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I want to show them that there is a greater scientist here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That I am the greatest scientist in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Navy acknowledges it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I become the top of the science department,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,my dream will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use my scientific knowledge to bring peace to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Master! We should be ashamed for suspecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the savior after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to abort the experiment now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If such a weapon explodes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,what's gonna happen to the people on the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you boneheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Navy's research facility!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy wants to kill as many pirates as they can
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and what they need is a weapon that will do it for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't want a weapon that would also kill civilians!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called collateral damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who get themselves involved must be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If we blow away everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we can bring peace to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to say I'm cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're using the damn prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as your guinea pigs as if they're real trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The incumbent fleet admiral, Sengoku, is too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But Admiral Red Hound would want a weapon that I make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you finally get it, then go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're disturbing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk must be jealous of me because I'm such a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he failed to turn people into giants again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make people bigger in a short period of time unless you use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I kept telling him:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He should just go kidnap some kids
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,who are still developing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and try every drug he can think of!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can talk to me like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost finished making a weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that you guys have only dreamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dismissed from the science department, Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eccentric behavior is intolerable and I can't protect you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk, the Navy, Straw Hat, and these guys right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,they're way less intelligent than me -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all dumb as a brick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate between C and B is closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate between D and B is closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can enter Building C and D from B Building now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Run like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
